# Blog Website

## © 2025 Arlind Ademaj

A simple **blog website** built with **Node.js**, **Express**, **EJS**, and **MongoDB**.  
This project allows users to view posts and manage content efficiently.

---

## Features

- Create, read, update, and delete blog posts (CRUD)
- Dynamic templates using **EJS**
- MongoDB for data storage
- Responsive and clean layout
- Easy to extend and customize

---

## Tech Stack

- **Node.js** – Backend runtime
- **Express** – Web framework
- **MongoDB** – Database
- **Mongoose** – MongoDB ODM
- **EJS** – Template engine
- **CSS** – Styling
